tify the eigenfrequencies of $\\mathcal{K}$\nfrom a given time series. It builds on the fact that the convergence of the\nrenormalized eigenvalues of the Gram matrix is a necessary and sufficient\ncondition for the existence of $\\mathcal{K}-$eigenfrequencies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Jul 2021 11:30:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Jul 2021 10:15:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 7 Nov 2021 18:18:25 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 26 Jan 2022 14:43:09 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 31 Jan 2022 12:52:44 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Thu, 3 Mar 2022 10:01:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-06"}
