{C}$V$_\\text{Si}^0$ by using the Huang-Rhys theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Jul 2021 12:22:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 27 Feb 2022 20:55:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-01"}
