ience cases, and detector\ndesign considerations including estimates of resolutions on DIS kinematic\nvariables. A possible road map toward the future MuIC and muon-antimuon\ncolliders is also presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Jul 2021 15:12:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Aug 2021 15:06:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-14"}
