 approaches to\nfacilitate quick and cost-effective drug repurposing. Such drugs could expand\nthe number of treatments available to patients who are not protected by\nvaccination.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Jul 2021 13:08:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2022 15:16:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-24"}
